#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. HTML: </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:0.3"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍa"
msgstr "Monks’ Undetermined"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:0.4"
msgid "1. Paṭhamaaniyatasikkhāpada"
msgstr "1. The first training rule"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-vp-pli3.187, pts-vp-en1.330, ms1V_1802 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:0.5"
msgid "Ime kho panāyasmanto dve aniyatā dhammā uddesaṃ āgacchanti."
msgstr "Venerables, these two undetermined rules come up for recitation."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc2, pts-cs-bu-an1.1, ms1V_1803 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī sāvatthiyaṃ kulūpako hoti, bahukāni kulāni upasaṅkamati."
msgstr "At that time Venerable Udāyī was associating with and visiting a number of families in Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato udāyissa upaṭṭhākakulassa kumārikā aññatarassa kulassa kumārakassa dinnā hoti."
msgstr "One of those families had given their daughter in marriage to the son of another family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā udāyī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena taṃ kulaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Just then, after robing up in the morning, Venerable Udāyī took his bowl and robe and went to the first of those families."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.5"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā manusse pucchi—"
msgstr "When he arrived, he asked"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.6"
msgid "“kahaṃ itthannāmā”ti?"
msgstr "where the daughter was,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.7"
msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "and he was told"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.8"
msgid "“dinnā, bhante, amukassa kulassa kumārakassā”ti."
msgstr "that she had been given to another family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.9"
msgid "Tampi kho kulaṃ āyasmato udāyissa upaṭṭhākaṃ hoti."
msgstr "That family too supported Venerable Udāyī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.10"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā udāyī yena taṃ kulaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He then went there"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.11"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā manusse pucchi—"
msgstr "and again asked"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.12"
msgid "“kahaṃ itthannāmā”ti?"
msgstr "where the girl was."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.13"
msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "They said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.14"
msgid "“esāyya, ovarake nisinnā”ti."
msgstr "“She’s sitting in her room.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.15"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā udāyī yena sā kumārikā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He approached that girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.16"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā tassā kumārikāya saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappesi kālayuttaṃ samullapanto kālayuttaṃ dhammaṃ bhaṇanto."
msgstr "and the two of them sat down alone on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it. When they were able, they just chatted; otherwise he gave her a teaching."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, pts-vp-pli3.188, ms1V_1804, pts-vp-en1.331
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.17"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena visākhā migāramātā bahuputtā hoti bahunattā arogaputtā aroganattā abhimaṅgalasammatā."
msgstr "At that time Visākhā Migāramātā had many healthy children and grandchildren, and she was considered very auspicious."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.18"
msgid "Manussā yaññesu chaṇesu ussavesu visākhaṃ migāramātaraṃ paṭhamaṃ bhojenti."
msgstr "At sacrifices, festivals, and celebrations people would feed Visākhā first."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.19"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nimantitā taṃ kulaṃ agamāsi."
msgstr "Just then she had been invited to the family that supported Venerable Udāyī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.20"
msgid "Addasā kho visākhā migāramātā āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ tassā kumārikāya saddhiṃ ekaṃ ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisinnaṃ."
msgstr "When she arrived, she saw him sitting alone with that girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.21"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and she said to him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.22"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ yaṃ ayyo mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappeti."
msgstr "“Venerable, it’s not appropriate that you should sit alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.23"
msgid "Kiñcāpi, bhante, ayyo anatthiko tena dhammena, api ca dussaddhāpayā appasannā manussā”ti."
msgstr "Although you may not be aiming at that act, people with little confidence are hard to convince.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.24"
msgid "Evampi kho āyasmā udāyī visākhāya migāramātuyā vuccamāno nādiyi."
msgstr "But Udāyī did not listen."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.25"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nikkhamitvā bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "After leaving, Visākhā told the monks about what had happened."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.26"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.27"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.28"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā udāyī mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappessatī”ti."
msgstr "“How can Venerable Udāyī sit alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4, ms1V_1805 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.29"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After rebuking Udāyī in many ways, they told the Master …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.30"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, udāyi, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappesī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, Udāyī, that you sat alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.31"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.32"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.33"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappessasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit alone with a woman on a such a seat?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.34"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.35"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.35a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc5, ms1V_1806, pts-vp-en1.332
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.36"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappeyya, tamenaṃ saddheyyavacasā upāsikā disvā tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya—"
msgstr "‘If a monk sits alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it, and a trustworthy female lay follower sees him and accuses him"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.37"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā, nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "of an offense entailing expulsion or an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing confession, then, if he admits to the sitting, he is to be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.38"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā, yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya, tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr "according to one of these three or according to what that trustworthy female lay follower has said."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:1.39"
msgid "Ayaṃ dhammo aniyato”ti."
msgstr "This rule is undetermined.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc6, pts-cs-bu-an1.2.1, ms1V_1807
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. HTML: </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc7, ms1V_1808
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.6"
msgid "Mātugāmo nāma"
msgstr "A woman:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.7"
msgid "manussitthī, na yakkhī na petī na tiracchānagatā."
msgstr "a human female, not a female spirit, not a female ghost, not a female animal;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.8"
msgid "Antamaso tadahujātāpi dārikā, pageva mahattarī."
msgstr "even a girl born that very day, all the more an older one."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc8, ms1V_1809
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.9"
msgid "Saddhinti"
msgstr "With:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.10"
msgid "ekato."
msgstr "together."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc9, ms1V_1810
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.11"
msgid "Eko ekāyāti"
msgstr "Alone:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.12"
msgid "bhikkhu ceva hoti mātugāmo ca."
msgstr "just the monk and the woman."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc10, ms1V_1811
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.13"
msgid "Raho nāma"
msgstr "Private:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.14"
msgid "cakkhussa raho, sotassa raho."
msgstr "there is private to the eye and there is private to the ear."

#. HTML: <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.15"
msgid "Cakkhussa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the eye"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.16"
msgid "na sakkā hoti akkhiṃ vā nikhaṇīyamāne bhamukaṃ vā ukkhipīyamāne sīsaṃ vā ukkhipīyamāne passituṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to see them winking, raising an eyebrow, or nodding."

#. HTML: </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.17"
msgid "Sotassa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the ear"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.18"
msgid "na sakkā hoti pakatikathā sotuṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to hear ordinary speech."

#. HTML: </span></span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc11, pts-vp-pli3.189, ms1V_1812
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.19"
msgid "Paṭicchannaṃ nāma"
msgstr "Concealed seat:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
#. VAR: kuṭṭena vā → kuḍḍena vā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.20"
msgid "āsanaṃ kuṭṭena vā kavāṭena vā kilañjena vā sāṇipākārena vā rukkhena vā thambhena vā kotthaḷiyā vā yena kenaci paṭicchannaṃ hoti."
msgstr "it is concealed by a wall, a screen, a door, a screening cloth, a tree, a pillar, a grain container, or anything else."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc12, ms1V_1813, pts-vp-en1.333
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.21"
msgid "Alaṃkammaniyeti"
msgstr "Suitable for doing it:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.22"
msgid "sakkā hoti methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevituṃ."
msgstr "one is able to have sexual intercourse."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc13, ms1V_1814
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.23"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ kappeyyāti"
msgstr "Sits:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.24"
msgid "mātugāme nisinne bhikkhu upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "the monk sits down or lies down next to the seated woman."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.25"
msgid "Bhikkhu nisinne mātugāmo upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "The woman sits down or lies down next to the seated monk."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.26"
msgid "Ubho vā nisinnā honti ubho vā nipannā."
msgstr "Both are seated or both are lying down."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc14, ms1V_1815
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.27"
msgid "Saddheyyavacasā nāma"
msgstr "Trustworthy:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.28"
msgid "āgataphalā abhisametāvinī viññātasāsanā."
msgstr "she has attained the fruit, she has broken through, she has understood the Teaching."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc15, ms1V_1816
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.29"
msgid "Upāsikā nāma"
msgstr "Female lay follower:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.30"
msgid "buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, saṃghaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā."
msgstr "she has gone for refuge to the Buddha, the Teaching, and the Order."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc16, ms1V_1817
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.31"
msgid "Disvāti"
msgstr "Sees:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.1.32"
msgid "passitvā."
msgstr "having seen."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term">
#. REF: sc17, pts-cs-bu-an1.2.2, ms1V_1818
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.1"
msgid "Tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya—"
msgstr "Accuses him of an offense"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.2"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "entailing expulsion or an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing confession,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.3"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "then, if he admits to the sitting, he is to be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.4"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "according to one of these three"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.5"
msgid "Yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr "or according to what that trustworthy female lay follower has said:"

#. HTML: </span></p><div class="gloss"><p>
#. REF: sc18, ms1V_1819 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.6"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.7"
msgid "“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nisinno mātugāmassa methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated, having sexual intercourse with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.8"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.9"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.10"
msgid "“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nisinno mātugāmassa methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated, having sexual intercourse with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.11"
msgid "so ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "but he says,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.12"
msgid "“saccāhaṃ nisinno, no ca kho methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevin”ti,"
msgstr "“It’s true that I was seated, but I didn’t have sexual intercourse,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.13"
msgid "nisajjāya kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the sitting."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.14"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.334
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.15"
msgid "“ayyo mayā diṭṭho nisinno mātugāmassa methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevanto”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated, having sexual intercourse with a woman,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.16"
msgid "so ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "but he says,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.17"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho nipanno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but lying down,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.18"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:2.2.19"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
